<DOC><DOCNO>  ZF108-280-356  </DOCNO><DOCID>08 280 356.andO;</DOCID><JOURNAL>InfoWorld  March 26 1990 v12 n13 p70(1).andM;</JOURNAL><TITLE>'It's Legal' helps users prepare legal documents with ease:well-conceived product is educational as well. (Software Review)(Parsons Technology Inc.'s software package) (evaluation)</TITLE><AUTHOR>Eckert, Jeff.andM;</AUTHOR><TEXT><ABSTRACT>Parsons Technology Inc's $49 It's Legal is a well-conceivedpackage that can help in constructing simple, legally bindingdocuments.andP;  It's Legal can help ordinary people help themselves bycreating living wills, simple wills, power of attorney, leases andpromissory notes.andP;  The program is on an easy to install floppy,with pull down menus for each of several documents.andP;  The programasks the user several questions which it then includes in thecreation of the document.andP;  It's Legal is not a substitute for anattorney on complex documents, but it can help create simple legalpapers.andM;</ABSTRACT></TEXT><DESCRIPT>Company:   Parsons Technology Inc. (products).andO;Product:   It's Legal (Computer program).andO;Topic:     EvaluationLegal ApplicationsDocument Preparation.andM;</DESCRIPT></DOC>